# Memory Index

This file serves as the catalog for the agent's experiential memory. It tracks
active memory files, archived entries, and the crystallization log.

## Structure

The memory directory is organized as follows:

```
memory/
├── YYYY-MM-DD.md          — Daily session notes (one file per active day)
├── decisions/             — Architecture Decision Records (ADR)
│   └── NNNN-title.md      — Numbered decision records
├── patterns/              — Observed patterns and heuristics
│   └── pattern-name.md    — Named pattern descriptions
└── errors/                — Error patterns and solutions
    └── error-name.md      — Named error pattern descriptions
```

### File Naming Conventions

- **Daily session notes:** `YYYY-MM-DD.md` (e.g., `2026-01-15.md`)
- **Decision records:** `NNNN-short-title.md` (e.g., `0001-use-fastapi-over-flask.md`)
- **Pattern descriptions:** `descriptive-kebab-case.md` (e.g., `retry-with-exponential-backoff.md`)
- **Error patterns:** `descriptive-kebab-case.md` (e.g., `python-output-buffering-trap.md`)

---

## Active Memory Files

| File | Topic | Last Updated | Status | Next Action |
|------|-------|-------------|--------|-------------|
| [YYYY-MM-DD.md] | [Topic description] | [Date] | Active / Awaiting crystallization | [Schedule crystallization / Monitor / Update] |
| [decisions/NNNN-title.md] | [Decision topic] | [Date] | Active | [Implement / Review / Archive] |
| [patterns/pattern-name.md] | [Pattern description] | [Date] | Active | [Crystallize into skill / Keep observing] |
| [errors/error-name.md] | [Error description] | [Date] | Active | [Crystallize into skill / Keep observing] |

**Status Definitions:**
- **Active:** Currently in use or recently updated.
- **Awaiting crystallization:** Contains extractable knowledge that has not yet been crystallized into a skill.

---

## Archived Memory Files

Memory files that have been crystallized into skills or are no longer actively referenced.

| File | Topic | Archived Date | Crystallized Into | Reason |
|------|-------|-------------|-------------------|--------|
| [YYYY-MM-DD.md] | [Topic] | [Date] | [skill-name] | Crystallized |
| [YYYY-MM-DD.md] | [Topic] | [Date] | N/A | Obsolete |

