## Crystallization Log

Record of all crystallization sessions and their outputs.

| Date | Source Files | Crystallized Into | Skills Created | Skills Updated | Operator |
|------|-------------|------------------|---------------|---------------|----------|
| [YYYY-MM-DD] | [List of memory files reviewed] | [Target skill files] | [Number] | [Number] | [Name] |
| [YYYY-MM-DD] | [List of memory files reviewed] | [Target skill files] | [Number] | [Number] | [Name] |

---

## Memory Health Metrics

Track these metrics to ensure the memory layer is healthy.

| Metric | Value | Target | Status |
|--------|-------|--------|--------|
| Total active memory files | [N] | 10-30 | OK / High / Low |
| Files awaiting crystallization | [N] | < 5 | OK / Backlog |
| Stale files (>14 days without update) | [N] | < 30% of total | OK / Needs attention |
| Average file age | [N days] | < 7 days for daily notes | OK / Stale |
| Crystallization sessions this month | [N] | >= 2 | OK / Behind schedule |
